<item>
            <title>[LU-7632] kernel update [RHEL7.2 3.10.0-327.4.4.el7]</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7632</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This update fixes the following bug:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Due to a regression, the NUMA node was not reported for PCI adapters, which&lt;br/&gt;
affected every IBM Power system deployed with Red Hat Enterprise Linux 7 and&lt;br/&gt;
caused significant decrease in the system performance. The underlying source&lt;br/&gt;
code has been patched, and the system performance no longer suffers in this&lt;br/&gt;
situation. (BZ#1283526)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
